How many degrees are in the smaller angle formed by the minute and hour hands on a clock at 12:30?

\begin{tikzpicture}[scale=0.8]
\draw (0,0) circle (2);
\foreach \i in {1,...,12} {
  \pgfmathsetmacro{\angle}{90 - \i*30}
  \node at ({1.6*cos(\angle)},{1.6*sin(\angle)}) {\i};
}
\foreach \i in {0,...,59} {
  \pgfmathsetmacro{\angle}{90 - \i*6}
  \draw ({1.9*cos(\angle)},{1.9*sin(\angle)}) -- ({2*cos(\angle)},{2*sin(\angle)});
}
\fill (0,0) circle (0.08);
\end{tikzpicture}
